  "page": "A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 8",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Tyrion III</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_dance_with_dragons\" title=\"A dance with dragons\"><img alt=\"ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" src=\"/images/7/79/ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"337\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ghoyan_Drohe\" title=\"Ghoyan Drohe\">Ghoyan Drohe</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n112 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_5\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 5\">Tyrion II</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_7\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 7\">Jon II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\">Tyrion III</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 9\">Davos I</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_14\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 14\">Tyrion IV</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_list\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character list</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_8&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>As dawn breaks <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> awakes to find the litter has stopped. He meets <a href=\"/index.php/Haldon\" title=\"Haldon\">Haldon</a> Halfmaester and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rolly_Duckfield\" title=\"Rolly Duckfield\">Rolly Duckfield</a>, who take on supplies from <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Illyrio\">Illyrio</a> before leaving with Tyrion. Illyrio tells them the dwarf's name is Yollo, although Tyrion, worried they will realize the name is a lie, claims it is his name in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> and his name is Hugor Hill. The pair tease Tyrion with tales of river <a href=\"/index.php/Pirates\" title=\"Pirates\">pirates</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Shrouded_Lord\" title=\"Shrouded Lord\">Shrouded Lord</a>. Tyrion and Haldon test each others' book knowledge while Duck recounts the events that led to his knighting at the hands of <a href=\"/index.php/Griff\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Griff\">Griff</a> and his unusual name. They ride until they reach the <a href=\"/index.php/Little_Rhoyne\" title=\"Little Rhoyne\">Little Rhoyne</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Ghoyan_Drohe\" title=\"Ghoyan Drohe\">Ghoyan Drohe</a>, where a poleboat, the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Shy_Maid\" title=\"Shy Maid\">Shy Maid</a>,</i> is waiting for them.\n</p><p>On board are the boy, <a href=\"/index.php/Young_Griff\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Young Griff\">Young Griff</a>, and his father, Griff. The older man reads a letter sent to him by <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Illyrio\">Illyrio</a>, telling of Tyrion's murder of his father. Griff is mistrustful and Tyrion is convinced he is no ordinary <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> - he can read, and he is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>, having knighted Duck himself. Tyrion promises to serve <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> faithfully, but asks \"What if we should find the queen and discover that this talk of dragons was just some sailor's drunken fancy? This wide world is full of such mad tales. Grumkins and snarks, ghosts and ghouls, mermaids, rock goblins, winged horses, winged pigs...winged lions.\" Griff tells him to guard his tongue or lose it.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_list\">Character list</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_8&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character list\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:6; column-width:300px;\"> \n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Haldon\" title=\"Haldon\">Haldon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rolly_Duckfield\" title=\"Rolly Duckfield\">Rolly Duckfield</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Griff\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Griff\">Griff</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Young_Griff\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Young Griff\">Young Griff</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Motho\" title=\"Motho\">Motho</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Zekko\" title=\"Zekko\">Zekko</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pono\" title=\"Pono\">Pono</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Serwyn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Serwyn\">Serwyn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Urrax\" title=\"Urrax\">Urrax</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Byron_Swann\" title=\"Byron Swann\">Byron Swann</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Syrax\" title=\"Syrax\">Syrax</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Munkun\" title=\"Munkun\">Munkun</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I